OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,FEverton have been ordered to pay
OL,8,FBurnley more than #35million in
OL,9,Fcompensation after they were sued over
OL,10,FPremier League profitability and
OL,11,Fsustainability breaches from the 2021-
OL,12,F22 season when the Clarets were
OL,13,Frelegated.
OL,15,FThe Toffees were deducted 10 points in
OL,16,Flate 2023 for financial misdemeanours,
OL,17,Fa punishment reduced to six points on
OL,18,Fappeal a few months later, under the
OL,19,Fprevious regime of Farhad Moshiri.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
