PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,FEverton finished four points above
OL,8,F18th-placed Burnley in 2021-22 but the
OL,9,FLancashire club successfully argued
OL,10,Fthat had the six-point penalty for PSR
OL,11,Fbreaches been applied that season then
OL,12,Fthey would have survived at the
OL,13,FToffees' expense.
OL,15,FAngry Everton officials have lodged an
OL,16,Fimmediate appeal at what they view as
OL,17,Fa "flawed" judgement.
OL,26,@yD@COUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,FIt is understood the club's hierarchy
OL,8,Fwere "astonished" by the ruling and
OL,9,Fbelieve it sets a dangerous precedent
OL,10,Ffor football as such a ruling would
OL,11,Fhave been "catastrophic" had the club
OL,12,Fnot got itself onto a more secure
OL,13,Ffinancial footing with the December
OL,14,F2024 takeover by The Friedkin Group.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@QO]sD@KOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
