FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,F"Everton Football Club is surprised
OL,8,Fand angered by the decision of a
OL,9,FPremier League Independent
OL,10,FDisciplinary Commission to order a
OL,11,Fcompensation payment to Burnley
OL,12,FFootball Club in relation to Everton's
OL,13,FPSR breach in June 2022," said a club
OL,14,Fstatement.
OL,16,F"Everton has appealed the decision and
OL,17,Fis clear in its belief the ruling is
OL,18,Ffundamentally flawed in both law and
OL,19,Ffact.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@YO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,F"The club does not recognise the
OL,8,Ffindings of the panel in determining
OL,9,FBurnley's relegation from the Premier
OL,10,FLeague in May 2022 was caused by a
OL,11,Fsporting advantage gained by Everton
OL,12,Fdue to a breach of Profit &
OL,13,FSustainability Rules, for which a
OL,14,Fsubstantive sporting sanction has
OL,15,Falready been received.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,F"This ruling sets a dangerous and
OL,8,Funworkable precedent for English
OL,9,Ffootball, given it is constructed on a
OL,10,Fprinciple that a club can be in breach
OL,11,Fof financial rules at any point in a
OL,12,Ffinancial year.
OL,14,F"Everton believes the panel's ruling
OL,15,Fmisrepresents the clear evidence
OL,16,Fpresented by its legal representatives
OL,17,Fand that an appeal will be successful."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,FEverton's compensation order was #26m,
OL,8,Fplus interest of #9.1m, but there is
OL,9,Fmore interest to be added on which
OL,10,Fcould take the total close to #40m.
OL,12,FBurnley are believed to have sought
OL,13,F#51.7m in recompense but Everton
OL,14,Ffundamentally disputed the calculation
OL,15,Fof the extent of the financial loss.
OL,17,FOther clubs had explored the
OL,18,Fpossibility of suing but did not
OL,19,Fproceed and there are no further cases
OL,20,Foutstanding against the club.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781115078
OL,3,CEverton ordered to pay Burnley
OL,4,Cmillions in compensation over
OL,5,Cfinancial breaches
OL,7,FEverton were judged to have overspent
OL,8,Fby #19.5m for the accounting period.
OL,9,FHowever, they argue they were unaware
OL,10,Fthey were going to be in breach and
OL,11,Fthere were six weeks between Burnley
OL,12,Fbeing relegated and the end of their
OL,13,Ffinancial year when they could have
OL,14,Ftaken steps to avoid the breach.
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
